532
00:23:28.365 --> 00:23:30.867
All right. Well. let's open it up
to. uh. some questions here.

533
00:23:30.951 --> 00:23:32.536
Um. Rachel.

534
00:23:32.619 --> 00:23:34.871
Coach. there were reports
that some within the organization

535
00:23:34.955 --> 00:23:37.416
