542
00:23:50.679 --> 00:23:52.556
You're joking
'cause you're better than him.

543
00:23:52.639 --> 00:23:57.477
Look. I'm gonna do the best I can.
and. uh. we… we hope it goes well.

544
00:23:57.561 --> 00:24:00.730
